324
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:39,640
Mm.

325
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,160
Is this your friend?

326
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:44,480
Oh, yeah.
We were modeling together.

327
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:46,520
Oh, Yim. This is Jamie,

328
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,560
