339
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:16,920
Are you hungry?

340
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,160
Let's have a meal.

341
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,200
Stir-fried garlic shrimp?

342
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:20,920
Mm.

343
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,640
Hm...

344
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:25,040
These guys are coming with us, though.

345
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:25,800
Is it cool with you?

346
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:26,960
Anything goes.

347
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:29,480
Oh, you're Qin, right?

348
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,440
I'm Yim.

349
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:33,960
Your friend is very handsome, Duang.

350
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,480
You might not remember me,

351
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,640
but back at Freshy Night,

352
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,400
