372
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:04,680
It'll be disastrous if we don't.

373
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:07,320
I know, but it'll be fine.

374
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:08,560
This will give me a good laugh.

375
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:14,720
Shall we get going?

376
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:17,480
Let's have a meal!

377
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,000
Thank you!

378
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,400
No need to rub salt into the wound.

379
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:33,480
What do we do now?

380
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:34,720
What are you waiting for?

381
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:37,110
Qin!

382
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:39,680
Come sit with me in the back.

383
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,960
I really want to sit next to you.

384
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,320
Let me take care of your stuff.

385
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:02,760
Do you have any films or series
you're trying to get into?

386
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:07,960
If you do, feel free
to recommend some to me.

387
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:10,920
Mm. I do, actually.

388
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:12,520
